{"tid":1822299,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈再進一步嘅方法","createTime":"2020-01-13T01:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T06:04:18.000Z","uid":295182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"824cf67e695c41543998395bd282f093dac34b77","tid":1822299,"uid":295182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"而家都係靠<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色APP</span>或者<span style=\"color: gold;\">人傳人</span>咁宣傳要去<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫襯黃色經濟圈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">可唔可以再進一步？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">每間<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃店</span>入面都會<span style=\"color: red;\">介紹埋該區附近嘅黃店</span>，鼓勵顧客去食佢地<br />\n<br />\n例如每張台都有張黃店menu..</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好處：</span></span><br />\n1）鼓勵香港人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">留喺黃色經濟圈消費</span></span>，去完其他黃店，其他黃店亦會叫返顧客要幫襯其他黃店，包括原現個啲黃店<br />\n<br />\n2）靠過黃店大家抱團互相幫助，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">打實黃色經濟圈嘅根基</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3）<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">增大宣傳</span></span>，幫助增大各間黃店嘅曝光率及增加客源<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">壞處：</span></span><br />\n1）送左顧客比其他黃店 <br />\n&lt;-如果本身間黃店係好味唔洗擔心無左個客啦<br />\n&lt;-如果本身間黃店唔好味又或者唔出名，更加需要大家互相宣傳幫手吸引客源啦<br />\n<br />\n打實左黃圈根基，到時甚至可以發展更多如黃圈優惠卷等等<br />\n<br />\n大家有無<span style=\"color: red;\">補充</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">點睇</span>？覺得好嘅幫p牌小弟推"},{"pid":"40485206c30b90bbaa2f0cdfab15a12648c8b7de","tid":1822299,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:16:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">有個黃app 係米被Play Store下架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f99ce4164e0d9171721d02038af322070862fba7","